<div class="intro">
  <p>
    Choose your tier, build your rig. Each level adds new component categories as your setup grows
    from a desk clamp to a full motion cockpit.
  </p>
  <p class="intro-disclaimer">Prices are estimates based on MSRP in USD and may not reflect current retail pricing. Always check the retailer before purchasing.</p>
</div>

{% include "wizard.njk" %}


{% include "tier-table.njk" %}

<div class="legend">
  <h3>How to read this table</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Tiers go from entry-level to extreme. Higher tiers introduce new component categories.</li>
    <li>A dash (<strong>&mdash;</strong>) means that category doesn't apply at this tier.</li>
    <li><em>Bundled</em> means the component is included with another purchase at that tier.</li>
    <li>Click any product name to expand details and links.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<section class="guides-section" id="guides">
  <h2 class="guides-heading">Guides</h2>
  <p class="guides-intro">Common questions answered. Know something we don't? <a href="https://github.com/twr-chris/simlanes">Submit a guide via PR.</a></p>
  <div class="guides-grid">
    {% for guide in collections.guides %}
    <a href="{{ guide.url }}" class="guide-card">
      <h3 class="guide-card-title">{{ guide.data.title }}</h3>
      {% if guide.data.description %}
      <p class="guide-card-desc">{{ guide.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      {% if guide.data.tags %}
      <div class="guide-card-tags">
        {% for tag in guide.data.tags %}
        <span class="guide-tag">{{ tag }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
